00:13:48,527 --> 00:13:52,793
Free enterprise
is a form of words

249
00:13:52,831 --> 00:13:55,561
that is intended
to conjure up in your mind

250
00:13:55,601 --> 00:14:00,538
a little town with different shops.

251
00:14:00,572 --> 00:14:03,507
