283
00:15:34,833 --> 00:15:38,860
We went to Catholic schools,
we lived a good life.

284
00:15:40,639 --> 00:15:43,972
If this was capitalism,
I loved it...

285
00:15:44,009 --> 00:15:46,477
and so did everyone else.

286
00:15:46,512 --> 00:15:50,505
During these years
a lot of people got rich

287
00:15:50,549 --> 00:15:54,542
and they had to pay
a top tax rate of 90%.

288
00:15:54,586 --> 00:15:56,679
90%?

289
