295
00:16:14,673 --> 00:16:17,073
Things seemed to be going
in the right direction.

296
00:16:17,109 --> 00:16:20,169
Dad had a secure job
and Mom could work

297
00:16:20,212 --> 00:16:22,646
if she wanted,
