419
00:23:12,657 --> 00:23:15,649
General Motors wouldn't be doing
anybody any service

420
00:23:15,694 --> 00:23:17,161
if it goes bankrupt.

421
00:23:17,195 --> 00:23:18,958
It has to do what it has to do

422
00:23:18,997 --> 00:23:22,194
in order to stay competitive
in today's economic climate.

423
00:23:22,233 --> 00:23:26,294
